To build the project from source:

mvn clean package -DskipTests=true


How to run the project:

1) change the absolute path to the blackbox executable in .../streamProcessingService/src/main/resources/application.properties 

2) run the jar by:

cd streamProcessingService/target 

java -jar streamProcessingService-1.0.jar

3) call the rest web service:

in a browser http://localhost:8080/counterAsynch

each click will show how the counter growths 
